WILLIAMS
v.
D'APOLITO 2018-0988 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's emergency motion for stay denied as moot.
